@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### HoloDex - fetch raw videos for Usada Pekora's channel
GET {{baseUrl}}/sync/test/holodex

### YouTube Data API - fetch raw channel data for the same channel
GET {{baseUrl}}/sync/test/youtube

### Twitch - resolve login to user_id, then fetch raw videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/sync/test/twitch

### Test get all
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vtubers

